<div aria-hidden="true" class="rah-static rah-static--height-zero SidebarWrapper" style="height:0;overflow:hidden"><div><div class="sc-2e8621ab-0 jdutDe sc-3ddd79c0-7 jAbpEx"><a href="/users/rupert-read" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 gnJVZv">Rupert Read</a><span><p>is emeritus associate professor of philosophy at the University of East Anglia in Norwich, UK, and a former political liaison, strategist and spokesperson for Extinction Rebellion. He is now co-director of the Climate Majority Project, which he co-founded, and the co-editor of <a href="https://londonpublishingpartnership.co.uk/climate-majority-project/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>The Climate Majority Project</em></a> (2024). He lives in Norfolk, UK.</p></span></div><br/><div class="sc-3ddd79c0-9 evnbsV"><p>Edited by<a href="/users/nigel-warburton" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 gnJVZv">Nigel Warburton</a></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-fb580250-0 bUjhzA"><span>4,400<!-- --> words</span><span class="sc-fb580250-1 cZHExZ"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="16" height="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-comment-bubble" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.303,16.553l1.107,3.783l-3.48-2.322c-0.689,0.234-1.422,0.371-2.193,0.371c-1.041,0-2.024-0.234-2.907-0.642 c2.034-1.697,3.333-4.275,3.333-7.166c0-1.994-0.625-3.836-1.677-5.347c0.406-0.073,0.823-0.117,1.251-0.117 c3.762,0,6.814,2.971,6.814,6.634c0,1.594-0.578,3.057-1.539,4.2L21.303,16.553z M15.255,10.684c0,3.861-3.213,6.99-7.176,6.99 c-0.812,0-1.583-0.144-2.31-0.391l-3.667,2.446l1.166-3.985l-0.744-0.638c-1.013-1.203-1.621-2.743-1.621-4.423 c0-3.858,3.215-6.987,7.176-6.987C12.042,3.696,15.255,6.825,15.255,10.684z"></path></svg><span>31<!-- --> <!-- -->comments</span></span><span class="sc-fb580250-2 foyURG"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="17" height="17" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999