 iOJnhy dFhhBp">Patrick J Casey</p></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-6 kQroYe"><span class="sc-d56bc236-7 ksqojN"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-comment-bubble" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.303,16.553l1.107,3.783l-3.48-2.322c-0.689,0.234-1.422,0.371-2.193,0.371c-1.041,0-2.024-0.234-2.907-0.642 c2.034-1.697,3.333-4.275,3.333-7.166c0-1.994-0.625-3.836-1.677-5.347c0.406-0.073,0.823-0.117,1.251-0.117 c3.762,0,6.814,2.971,6.814,6.634c0,1.594-0.578,3.057-1.539,4.2L21.303,16.553z M15.255,10.684c0,3.861-3.213,6.99-7.176,6.99 c-0.812,0-1.583-0.144-2.31-0.391l-3.667,2.446l1.166-3.985l-0.744-0.638c-1.013-1.203-1.621-2.743-1.621-4.423 c0-3.858,3.215-6.987,7.176-6.987C12.042,3.696,15.255,6.825,15.255,10.684z"></path></svg></span></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><footer class="sc-8723d312-0 fVfKHB footer" data-test="footer"><div class="sc-ae266dcd-0 sc-8723d312-1 bwTVbW dRXxEN"><div class="sc-70ed4693-0 bxMjPi"><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/essays" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Essays</a><a href="/ideas" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Ideas</a><a href="/videos" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Videos</a></nav></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/about" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">About</a><a href="/contact" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Contact</a><a href="/support" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Support</a></nav></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC gSiEIv"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/feed.rss" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">RSS Feed</a><a data-ga-select-promotion="aeon_footer_donate" href="/donate" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Donate</a><a href="/community-guidelines" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Community Guidelines</a></nav></div></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-461fb0e3-0 d